OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome evening sunshine to start with.
OL,7,FClear spells allow patchy fog or frost
OL,8,Fto develop in west overnight, while
OL,9,Flow cloud and mist gradually return to
OL,10,Fthe east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAny overnight mist or fog
OL,13,Flifting through the morning. Staying
OL,14,Fdry but much cooler with variable
OL,15,Fcloud in the east. Still warm with
OL,16,Fprolonged spells of sunshine in the
OL,17,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
